        "height": 256,
        "content": "### 1) Hashtag & Cookie Selection  \n**What it does**  \n• Downloads cookie list → **Select Cookie** (GPT-4o) picks one based on time slice.  \n• **AI Agent** creates a realistic AI/BPA hashtag.\n\n**Credentials**  \nOpenAI + SharePoint OAuth2.\n\n**Tweaks**  \n• Edit prompt for different niches.  \n• Add/remove cookies in SharePoint file."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
