      ],
      "parameters": {
        "width": 432,
        "height": 304,
        "content": "### 2) Tweet Scraping & Deduplication  \n**What it does**  \n• Runs Phantombuster Hashtag Agent → gets ~10 tweets.  \n• Chooses one at random, compares with `twitter_posts_already_liked.csv`.\n\n**Credentials**  \nPhantombuster API + SharePoint OAuth2.\n\n**Tweaks**  \n• Increase `ENV_SEARCH_RESULTS_PER_LAUNCH` to scan more tweets.  \n• Change duplicate logic inside **Check if in List**."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "5e2eb2d6-8d08-4671-b3b0-ed98803a1d41",
      "name": "Sticky Note7",
