      ],
      "parameters": {
        "width": 464,
        "height": 272,
        "content": "### 3) CSV Upload & Auto-like Launch  \n**What it does**  \n• Creates a 1-row CSV with the chosen tweet URL.  \n• Uploads it to SharePoint and passes the public link to the Autolike Agent.\n\n**Credentials**  \nSharePoint OAuth2 + Phantombuster API.\n\n**Tweaks**  \n• Change file/folder names in **Upload CSV**.  \n• Replace SharePoint with another storage provider."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
