        "content": "### 4) Rate Limiting & Scheduling  \n**What it does**  \n• Hourly **Schedule Trigger** plus **Wait** nodes throttle launches to ≈1 000 likes/day.\n\n**Credentials**  \nNone\n\n**Tweaks**  \n• Edit the cron rule or `Wait` durations to meet your own limits.  \n• Remove **Wait** nodes if Phantombuster limits are higher on your plan."
